    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. You won't find another one this clean out there. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a concours-grade example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the desirable wide-body chassis and integrated AWD system. The 3.6L flat-six delivers a linear power band via VarioCam Plus, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical provenance is impeccable; the IMS bearing has been upgraded to a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal remains perfectly dry. The suspension retains factory-spec geometry with no bushing deflection, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors with zero lip. The Arctic Silver Metallic finish shows consistent paint depth across all panels, and the interior's supple leather remains free of UV damage or bolster compression. A DME report confirms a clean history with no over-revs in high ranges, ensuring the valvetrain integrity remains uncompromised.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
