    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, while the original floor mats have been protected by custom liners. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard with a full service history available for inspection. From the crystal-clear headlights to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in brand-new performance tires, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a pristine, investment-grade example of automotive history.",
