      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically pristine and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
