      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. The powerplant features individual throttle bodies and delivers linear torque up to a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining factory-spec rigidity with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a hydraulic steering rack that offers unparalleled feedback. Comprehensive mechanical provenance includes addressed rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are in peak operating condition. The M-Variable Differential Lock and subframe bushings exhibit zero play, providing a surgical level of cornering precision. This is a museum-grade specimen for the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity.",
